{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"59f6eca9f1","title":"讽刺社会主义的反动诗——忆元旦","origin":"《揭穿右派分子的丑恶面目》（内部资料　注意保存，中共云南省委整风领导小组办公室编印，1957年9月3日）","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3c52a2f3ad","index":0,"year":1956,"month":12,"day":24,"articleId":"59f6eca9f1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9b57a01b04","name":"云南"},{"id":"dcc65143c7","name":"栗树"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bf0806ed79","type":"title","text":"讽刺社会主义的反动诗——忆元旦","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"7033ee6d58","type":"authors","text":"云南栗树","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"72ba121ce0","type":"subtitle","text":"(栗树：云南省供销社干部)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"ae6f3842e0","type":"subtitle","text":"忆元旦","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"bcdf208594","type":"paragraph","text":"阴沉沉的天空","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"21b1c3ca78","type":"paragraph","text":"洒着牛毛般的细雨","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"9c906665be","type":"paragraph","text":"雪花下得象梅花似","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"842367a397","type":"paragraph","text":"象秋枝的落叶飘落地上","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"c595ae74c9","type":"paragraph","text":"满天的乌云","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"72d2c6bd36","type":"paragraph","text":"衬托出宇宙的阴暗","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"5ecfa8e20f","type":"paragraph","text":"这就是元旦的前夕","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"9c64c4f51e","type":"paragraph","text":"也就是元旦的晚装","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"b642c84799","type":"paragraph","text":"这就是人们在睡梦的想往","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"3004e8a16b","type":"paragraph","text":"一长排的人群","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"20549a83bc","type":"paragraph","text":"在拥挤嘈杂的人声中","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"e0efa665d2","type":"paragraph","text":"不时隐约传来口声","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"517064b42a","type":"paragraph","text":"我买到二两肉，他买到一两油","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"c91f81d472","type":"paragraph","text":"人们拿这一两香油二两肉来渡过这寒冷的元旦","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"f165335bf2","type":"paragraph","text":"虽然这样……","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"edd9363eb7","type":"paragraph","text":"但是人民还是在为着生活而挣扎着","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"02e443c162","type":"paragraph","text":"等着即将来临的一年比一年更美好的新的明天","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"3dcda82855","type":"paragraph","text":"何草不黄，何日不行，何人不想","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"9e7387c779","type":"paragraph","text":"我也在想……","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"f56d0fcf55","type":"paragraph","text":"往年的元旦，我穿着黄军装","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"b22fdc0464","type":"paragraph","text":"今年的元旦，我穿上了蓝干装","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"7ff5395e64","type":"paragraph","text":"黄黄的军装，蓝蓝的干部装","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"4b7ea4cd26","type":"paragraph","text":"也不过如此，也不过这样","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"a6cd52e8ac","type":"paragraph","text":"在元旦来临的前夕","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"8da24fdc4b","type":"paragraph","text":"用我拿枪的手，再拿起笔杆","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"7c0a5910f1","type":"paragraph","text":"来忆元旦","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"b16d404269","type":"paragraph","text":"虽只片断","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"62bc777689","type":"paragraph","text":"但掺杂了多少的想……","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"d76c3c55ce","type":"paragraph","text":"在想一年比一年即将来临的","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"d586e077c8","type":"paragraph","text":"美好的、新的生活、新的元旦，怎不使我忆想。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"},{"id":"ee6683d596","type":"paragraph","text":" 56年12月","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1"}],"page":{"id":"69655b8a78","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59f6eca9f1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}